## Review Protocol

Before any PR, review:

1. **Ticket re-read** — verify every scenario addressed
2. **Cross-layer consistency** — grep every new field across all layers
3. **Enum completeness** — verify switch/case handles all values
4. **Transaction safety** — trace every write caller
5. **Race condition analysis** — trace concurrent flows
6. **Test scenario completeness** — every branch has a test
7. **Pre-existing vs introduced** — distinguish prior warnings from new ones
8. **Security** — new external calls, data exposure, unsafe defaults
9. **100/100 confidence gate** — do not proceed to MR until all above pass

